title: Vanderbilt, Derek Mason get first SEC win
text: Vanderbilt, Derek Mason get first SEC win Adam Sparks , asparks@tennessean.com 6:36 p.m. CDT October 24, 2015 Buy Photo Vanderbilt cornerback Tre Herndon (31) breaks up a pass intended for Missouri wide receiver J'Mon Moore (6) to seal Vanderbilt's 10 to 3 victory against Missouri with seconds remaining in the fourth quarter at Vanderbilt Stadium Saturday Oct. 24, 2015, in Nashville, Tenn.
